imgDesc.text:
A form of Phlogiston that resembles a gas. In essence, it is still Phlogiston, and it contains massive amounts of heat, making it very dangerous. While in Wind Currents formed by gaseous Phlogiston or areas with large amounts of gaseous Phlogiston, you will be burned by the high temperatures.
However, <color=#ffe14b>Qucusaurs</color> and some members of the <color=#ffe14b>Flower-Feather Clan</color> have mastered the art of using gaseous Phlogiston without getting burned.
